        <!-- About Section -->
        <div class="container-xxl py-5 mt-4">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row g-5 align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
                        <img class="img-fluid rounded-4 shadow" src="img/Kualakubs-about-section-image.jpg"
                            alt="About Us" style="border-radius: 20px;">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
                        <h6 class="bg-white text-start pe-3 text-uppercase fw-bold"
                            style="color: #60b457; letter-spacing: 2px;">ABOUT</h6>
                        <h1 class="mb-3 fw-bold" style="color: rgb(61, 6, 75);">Kualakubs School</h1>
                        <h5 class="mb-4 text-dark fw-bold">Making learning a joy for little ones.</h5>
                        <p class="mb-4">Kualakubs is a proud initiative of the Geeta Group of Institutions, a respected
                            name in Indian education since 1985. With a strong legacy across preschools, K–12 schools,
                            higher education institutes, and a university, the Group brings decades of academic
                            excellence and trust to early childhood education.
                        </p>
                        <p class="mb-4">At Kualakubs, we believe that the early years lay the foundation for a child’s
                            lifelong love for learning. Our thoughtfully designed curriculum is research-informed,
                            developmentally appropriate, and focused on building strong concepts through play,
                            exploration, and phonics-based learning.</p>
                        <p class="mb-4">Loved by parents and educators alike, Kualakubs offers a nurturing environment
                            where children feel safe, confident, and inspired—making learning not just effective, but
                            truly joyful.

                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

